summary: Now you can enjoy a nice cold Cliff Racer or the silky smooth Velvet LeChance and then top it off with a soothing yet refreshing White-Gold Tower; specialty drinks from Talen-jei, our trusty Argonian bartender found in the Bee and Barb in Riften. So come on down try to The Bee and Barb and try them all!
descriptionHtml:
This is a patch for Imp's More Complex Needs that adds Talen-Jei's drinks which are:Â Cliff Racer Velvet LeChance White-Gold Tower.
These drinks now appear as food in your inventory instead of potions and can be drunk just like the rest of IMCN drinks with the same drunk effects.
If you found your way to this webpage, I assume you allready have Imp's More Complex Needs installed. If not here is a link for this most excellent mod:

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10639/?

Go get it allready!
